snippet.title: Shell of a King - Gameplay Trailer v1.1
snippet.description:
Test your strength in Shell of a King! A precision bullet-hell adventure that will push your dodging skills to the limit. 

Available now on Steam in Early Access:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2384130/?snr=1_5_9__205

Join the Official Discord for new, updates, playtest access, and more!
https://discord.gg/gT6R4rBxAx
